{{en-proper noun}}

# {{senseid|en|Q83958}}An ancient [[Greek]] kingdom, located to the north of [[Thessaly]], comprising the Greek city of [[Thessaloniki]] and its surroundings.
#: {{syn|en|Macedon}}
# {{senseid|en|Q81734}}The largest and second-most populous [[region]] of [[Greece]], comprising the regions of [[West Macedonia]], [[Central Macedonia]] and the East Macedonia part of the region of [[East Macedonia and Thrace]].
# {{senseid|en|Q221}}The [[Republic of North Macedonia]], a country in Southeastern [[Europe]].
